weapons.name: W-Engine 12001
weapons.shortDescription: A W-Engine that prioritizes damage output over noise reduction. It can indiscriminately deal considerable damage to all units nearby.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12002
weapons.shortDescription: A W-Engine with excellent sonic and thermal energy usage, capable of hitting its target with a double whammy.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12003
weapons.shortDescription: A high-capacity portable W-Engine that can collect dissipated energy from its surroundings, thus enhancing the combat effectiveness of its operator.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12004
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine featuring a built-in sonic generator that boosts its damage output.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12005
weapons.shortDescription: A standardized W-Engine with balanced performance that enhances its owner's and their teammates' combat effectiveness in all aspects.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12006
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine that features motion capture algorithms, which enhance the overall combat competency of your squad.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12007
weapons.shortDescription: An energy-storage type W-Engine with a unique operation circuit. It will absorb scattered energy up to a certain amount before unleashing it all at once.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12008
weapons.shortDescription: A tactical W-Engine that locates enemies using high-frequency sound waves. Its aiming aid can make its operator's precision attack more deadly.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12009
weapons.shortDescription: A frequency-converting W-Engine that can quickly generate excessive power and effectively increase its user's battle prowess.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12010
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine that can analyze the target's weak spots through real-time calculations.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12011
weapons.shortDescription: A damage-type W-Engine that features an enhanced movement detection module that can quickly alter its output intensity to optimize battle efficiency.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12012
weapons.shortDescription: A high-capacity W-Engine that features a built-in generator, which allows it to keep a stable storage of electrical power.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12013
weapons.shortDescription: A W-Engine with a component structure adjusted according to specific parameters. It can enhance the defensive capabilities of those who have a certain style of combat.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12014
weapons.shortDescription: A functional W-Engine that specializes in energy conversion. It can analyze combat environments and generate special sounds to disrupt the enemy's offense.

weapons.name: W-Engine 12015
weapons.shortDescription: A W-Engine with a built-in heating component. When operating at high speeds, it resembles a blazing blue flame.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13001
weapons.shortDescription: A custom-made W-Engine designed for urban music lovers. It sacrifices heat dissipation components for improved sound quality.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13002
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine equipped with a high-speed camera module. The best choice for in-Hollow photography enthusiasts.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13003
weapons.shortDescription: A consumer-class W-Engine launched by an exotic pet fan club to promote pet culture. Due to its cute appearance, it was once a very popular model.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13004
weapons.shortDescription: A damage-type W-Engine made of special Etheric matter. When its user is attacked, it builds up energy.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13005
weapons.shortDescription: A high-power W-Engine that boasts a cutting-edge energy conversion system. It collects excess heat and supplies it to the steamer.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13006
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine whose outer shell is made of composite Etheric matter that effectively absorbs impact, and turns it against the enemy.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13007
weapons.shortDescription: An epic W-Engine favored by Starlight Knight fans. Its high popularity and scarcity marketing strategy have caused an influx of knock-offs.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13008
weapons.shortDescription: A W-Engine produced by recycling abandoned Bangboo shells. Its electrode cores made of recycled metals can release high-voltage charges.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13009
weapons.shortDescription: This damage-type W-Engine boasts a built-in current transformer, and automatically attracts electrically sensitive objects around the operator and deals additional damage to them.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13010
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine decorated with a fluffy bunny. However, it is just an imitation of the real animal.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13011
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine equipped with a temperature regulator where residual heat generated by the W-Engine's high frequency is funneled into the hot springs on its surface.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13012
weapons.shortDescription: The W-Engine, with its bright colors and great performance, saw poor sales at first because it resembled a toy. But with its reasonable price, it slowly gained a positive reputation.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13013
weapons.shortDescription: A W-Engine with a grandiose and luxurious appearance equipped with a premium Ether-powered anti-theft device. It's actually used to provide the equipper with energy.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13014
weapons.shortDescription: Designed for those Hollow-dwelling bards who refuse to listen to the same albums repeatedly, this W-Engine comes equipped with a radio module that can transform Etheric frequencies into melodies.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13015
weapons.shortDescription: Gather 'round, mortals! Turn up the music!

weapons.name: W-Engine 13016
weapons.shortDescription: Clearly a W-Engine is for sound, and not images. What kind of lunatic genius would insist on stuffing a 16mm film camera into a W-Engine?

weapons.name: W-Engine 13019
weapons.shortDescription: Countless threads of Sword Will echo through this tiny stretch of sky.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13101
weapons.shortDescription: A customized W-Engine that focuses on energy storage, modified to improve its energy capacity. This model is often used by Anby.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13103
weapons.shortDescription: A cost-effective W-Engine that can store energy, with improvements made to its internal space. This model is often used by Nicole.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13106
weapons.shortDescription: An enhanced W-Engine with a high rotation speed. A chainsaw has been integrated into its shaft. This model is often used by Corin.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13108
weapons.shortDescription: A customized supercomputing W-Engine, specialized in aim support and ballistic calculations. Modified by Billy, it now looks like some sort of knock-off Starlight Knight figurine.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13111
weapons.shortDescription: Originally a rev-enhanced W-Engine, it has been modified by Anton with the most expensive rotary drill parts that allow it to exceed its output limits.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13112
weapons.shortDescription: A powerful protection-type W-Engine, characterized by thick oil cylinders that ceaselessly roar inside it. It can provide sufficient power for heavy machinery.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13113
weapons.shortDescription: An intricate W-Engine developed by Section 6 and later modified with extra features. It can control Ether particles to form an energy field. This model is favored by Soukaku.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13115
weapons.shortDescription: A support W-Engine propelled by jets that is both mobile and impactful, it can traverse the entire battlefield providing combat buffs.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13127
weapons.shortDescription: A defensive W-Engine independently researched and created by Public Security which simplifies the offensive components to enhance the energy conversion ability in its shield.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13128
weapons.shortDescription: An energy W-Engine modded from spare parts of a truck's engine. It converts the original cylinder into an energy storage unit, which is highly advantageous.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13135
weapons.shortDescription: An energy W-Engine modded from spare parts of a truck's engine. It converts the original cylinder into an energy storage unit, which is highly advantageous.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13142
weapons.shortDescription: Pressing acupoints is like cooking. Striking the fatal acupoint is like setting the stove on fire, bringing disaster.

weapons.name: W-Engine 13144
weapons.shortDescription: A flame both fierce and faithful, burning without end.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14001
weapons.shortDescription: A high-performance supercomputing W-Engine, capable of collecting real-time battlefield data and equipped with mini cannons.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14002
weapons.shortDescription: A new supercomputing W-Engine, featuring cutting-edge integrated chips that dynamically monitor the battlefield and provide tactical analysis for the user.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14003
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine modeled after a revolver. It can load bullet-shaped condensed Ether batteries, which release a great amount of power when fired.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14102
weapons.shortDescription: A supercomputing W-Engine equipped with a motion monitoring feature. Thanks to Nekomata's modifications, it perfectly matches the fast reflexes and combat maneuvers of feline Thirens.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14104
weapons.shortDescription: A W-Engine made for Soldier 11 by Obsidian Division. Its intense heat can be used to clear the entire battlefield.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14105
weapons.shortDescription: In chasing illusions, she was entranced by the light that pierced through the mist.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14107
weapons.shortDescription: A versatile W-Engine based on a motorcycle tire that Big Daddy made for Caesar.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14109
weapons.shortDescription: Hail falls before the shrine, waking her. The blizzard is coming.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14110
weapons.shortDescription: A functional W-Engine with ultra-high power capacity. Modified by Koleda, its energy level has almost exceeded the safety limit.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14114
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine with a powerful temperature control system. Modified by Lycaon, it has the capability to quickly create extremely cold environments.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14116
weapons.shortDescription: A violent W-Engine that can ignite flames with a siphon. It deals simple and crude burn damage, encouraging relentless, bone-crushing follow-up attacks.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14117
weapons.shortDescription: Modified by Burnice, this W-Engine uses a special fuel as its power source to boost combustion performance to the max.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14118
weapons.shortDescription: The latest W-Engine that possesses a hypercalculation core. It can compile operational codes for machines at top speed. This model is favored by Grace.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14119
weapons.shortDescription: A high-power W-Engine that possesses efficient freezing capabilities and high damage output. This model is often used by Ellen.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14120
weapons.shortDescription: Bitterness and pain beget hope, and he devours them all.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14121
weapons.shortDescription: A special W-Engine with multiple layers embedded inside. It can quickly recharge 	special-model Bangboo and custom-made combat equipment. This model is favored by Rina.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14122
weapons.shortDescription: A new model of supercomputing W-Engine custom-made by HSO Section 6, equipped with the most elite calculation and analysis functions.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14124
weapons.shortDescription: The latest tactical W-Engine used by Public Security's elite Hollow squads, possessing a powerful Ether energy source. It's Zhu Yuan's favored model.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14125
weapons.shortDescription: A custom stun W-Engine made for an Automaton referencing the combat style and abilities of one. Energy is stored within, then lashes outwards upon conversion.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14126
weapons.shortDescription: A deadly W-Engine from unknown sources, modified personally by Jane Doe with the intent to deal severe physical damage and Anomaly.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14129
weapons.shortDescription: Shadowed by darkness at every step, he laid bare his heart to kindle a single, flickering flame.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14130
weapons.shortDescription: She lingers by the banks of the Styx, waiting for the tide to extinguish the fury burning in her chamber.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14131
weapons.shortDescription: Underneath the radiant splendor, her genuine self has never been hidden.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14132
weapons.shortDescription: The sound of the strings, sharp as blades, cut through the night, protecting the one.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14133
weapons.shortDescription: A bird landed on the windowsill, scattering starlight from its tail feathers.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14134
weapons.shortDescription: Not too sweet, and not too cold.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14136
weapons.shortDescription: Broken eyes hold both resilience and vulnerability.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14137
weapons.shortDescription: The world is vast and full of change, and fate is unpredictable. But regardless of hardship or lack thereof, one must stay true to one's heart.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14138
weapons.shortDescription: The sheen of silver is not innocence. Can the blades of the past cut through fate's connections?

weapons.name: W-Engine 14139
weapons.shortDescription: The warm fire blazes through the long night, casting light on the tiger's roar in my heart.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14140
weapons.shortDescription: Starlight became her blade, and she held courage and love firmly in her hands.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14141
weapons.shortDescription: A masterfully crafted design, infused with the creator's pursuit of beauty.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14143
weapons.shortDescription: The world may change, but my heart remains constant, like clouds standing eternal.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14145
weapons.shortDescription: After countless years, it remains a silent puzzle.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14146
weapons.shortDescription: Her journey continues along the long, endless circle.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14147
weapons.shortDescription: The purging flames burned a hundred times, yet never cleansed me.

weapons.name: W-Engine 14148
weapons.shortDescription: That call you never picked up... she's the one who answered it.
